nodes.text: This white-skinned species was a sentient species of bipedals that possessed three-fingered hands, webbed toes and glowing blue eyes.

During the Clone Wars, three members of this species, who were saboteurs affiliated with the Confederacy of Independent Systems, were present on Coruscant. Posing as astromech technicians, the three individuals planted a bomb inside R2-D2 in an attempt to destroy the Senate Chamber.
